 ‘Get up. Continue your journey ahead of the people, so that they may enter and possess the land I swore to give their ancestors.’ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 1:35","book":"Deu","chapter":1,"verse":35,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 1:35","book":"Deu","chapter":1,"verse":35}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:10:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“And now, Israel, what does the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God ask of you except to fear "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 14:23","book":"Deu","chapter":14,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God by walking in all his ways, to love him, and to worship the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God with all your heart and all your soul? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 6:5","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 11:13","book":"Deu","chapter":11,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 13:3","book":"Deu","chapter":13,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 30:6","book":"Deu","chapter":30,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 22:5","book":"Jos","chapter":22,"verse":5,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 22:37","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":37,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 14:23","book":"Deu","chapter":14,"verse":23},{"label":"Dt 6:5","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":5},{"label":"Dt 11:13","book":"Deu","chapter":11,"verse":13},{"label":"Dt 13:3","book":"Deu","chapter":13,"verse":3},{"label":"Dt 30:6","book":"Deu","chapter":30,"verse":6},{"label":"Jos 22:5","book":"Jos","chapter":22,"verse":5},{"label":"Mt 22:37","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":37}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:10:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Keep the "},{"kind":"text","text"